Scope of this license

The MIT license above covers only the source code in this repository.

It does not cover the Commodore 64 ROM images (KERNAL, BASIC, and the character
generator ROM) or the 1541 DOS ROM. Those are copyrighted by their respective
owners, are not included in this repository, and are not distributed with this
software. To run the emulator you must supply your own copies from a legally
obtained source.

Disk images, cartridges, and any other software used with this emulator are
likewise not covered by this license.
